com.google.gcloud.bigquery

Class JobInfo<S extends JobStatistics>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.gcloud.bigquery.JobInfo<S>
  • Type Parameters:
    S - the statistics type
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CopyJobInfo, ExtractJobInfo, LoadJobInfo, QueryJobInfo

    public abstract class JobInfo<S extends JobStatistics>
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Base class for Google BigQuery Job information. Jobs are objects that manage asynchronous tasks such as running queries, loading data, and exporting data. Use CopyJobInfo for a job that copies an existing table. Use ExtractJobInfo for a job that exports a table to Google Cloud Storage. Use LoadJobInfo for a job that loads data from Google Cloud Storage into a table. Use QueryJobInfo for a job that runs a query.
    See Also:
    Jobs, Serialized Form
